config BR2_PACKAGE_RHAD
	bool "R.H.A.D."
	select BR2_PACKAGE_BLUEZ
	default n
	help
	  The Remote Hardaware Abstraction Daemon (R.H.A.D) 
	  provides an interface to the AS Layer to perfom the Sky 
	  specific bluetooth operations like diagnostics, FindMe, 
	  TV Code configuration, Remote Upgrade etc.
	  The R.H.A.D receives messages from the AS Layer, 
	  understands the message and routes it to the appropriate
	  entity ie, the BlueZ daemon or the corresponding vendor daemon.
